# Install UFW firewall
`apt install ufw`

# Enable UFW correctly
`ufw allow in 22/tcp`
`ufw allow out 22/tcp`
`ufw allow in 80/tcp`
`ufw allow out 80/tcp`
`ufw allow out 443/tcp`
`ufw allow in 443/tcp`
`ufw allow out 25/tcp`
`ufw allow out 110/tcp`

# Verify UFW state
`ufw status verbose`

# Enable firewall
`ufw enable`
